item.title: Playerform patch?
item.dc:creator: @aznph8playa aznph8playa
item.description:
@aznph8playa wrote:

[quote=“Weibs, post:2, topic:20899”]did you overwrite the old playerform? When you download the patch, you need to go into the
SRL > SRL > Misc folder, and then save with the same name as the old PlayerForm include. It will ask you if you want to replace it, and say ‘yes’. I’m guessing that you have the old version and patch, just in two different places.[/quote]

I’m having the same problem yet I can’t figure out what the old PlayerForm include was. I made a few edits to PlayerForm to fix the problems it brought up but I’m not sure they worked:
